msgctxt "212_Haruka"
msgid "You looked really cool, Uncle Kaz!"
msgstr "¡Te viste súper genial, Tío Kaz!"

msgctxt "224_Haruka"
msgid "You're amazing, Uncle Kaz! You're like a real baseball player!"
msgstr "¡Eres increíble, Tío Kaz! ¡Juegas como un beisbolista profesional!"

msgctxt "248_Kiryu"
msgid "(Haruka sure is happy...)"
msgstr "(Haruka parece feliz...)."

msgctxt "284_Haruka"
msgid "Thanks for doing all that stuff for me, Uncle Kaz!"
msgstr "¡Gracias por hacer todo eso por mí, Tío Kaz!"

msgctxt "296_Haruka"
msgid "Here, this is a special present, just for you!"
msgstr "¡Aquí tienes un regalo especial, sólo para ti!"

msgctxt "368_Haruka"
msgid "Oh, you were so close! Let's try again!"
msgstr "¡Ay, casi lo logras! ¡Intentémoslo otra vez!"

msgctxt "380_Haruka"
msgid "But I wanted to see you try it..."
msgstr "Pero yo quería verte intentarlo..."

msgctxt "392_Haruka"
msgid "Aw... That was close!"
msgstr "Ay... ¡Eso estuvo cerca!"

msgctxt "428_Haruka"
msgid "Uncle Kaz! Get 4,000 points in an Extra Hard Game!"
msgstr "¡Tío Kaz! ¡Consigue 4,000 puntos en el Modo Extra Difícil!"

